<table><tr><td>James PA, Oparil S, Carter BL, Cushman WC, Dennison-Himmelfarb C, Handler J, Lackland DT, LeFevre ML, MacKenzie TD, Ogedegbe O, Smith SC Jr, Svetkey LP, Taler SJ, Townsend RR, Wright JT Jr, Narva AS, Ortiz E. 2014 evidence-based guideline for the management of high blood pressure in adults: report from the panel members appointed to the Eighth Joint National Committee (JNC 8). JAMA. 2014 Feb 5;311(5):507-20. [45 references] <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712211501/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=24352797" target="_blank">PubMed</a> <img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712211501im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712211501/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=48192&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fjama.jamanetwork.com%252farticle.aspx%253farticleid%253d1791497">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712211501im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
