 (372586001), <a href="/web/20180712211501/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0012802&amp;fLockTerm=Thiazide+diuretic">Thiazide diuretic</a>
 (372747003), <a href="/web/20180712211501/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0012802&amp;fLockTerm=Thiazide+diuretic">Thiazide diuretic</a>
 (45518007)                    </div>
                    <!-- /.field-content -->
                </div>
                <!-- /.field -->
    </div>
